---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy – Cadre" description="Cadre privacy policy.">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24">
      <a href="/" class="inline-block mb-12">
        <img src="/images/logo-wordmark.svg" alt="Cadre" class="h-10 w-auto" />
      </a>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-[-0.03em] text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] space-y-6">
        <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 9, 2026</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mt-8">What we collect</h2>
        <p>When you join our waitlist, we collect your email address, IP address (for fraud prevention), and optionally your use case and hosting provider preference.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mt-8">How we use it</h2>
        <p>We use your email to send you waitlist confirmation and launch updates. We use survey data to prioritize product development. We do not sell your data to third parties.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mt-8">Where your data lives</h2>
        <p>Your waitlist data is stored in a PostgreSQL database hosted by Hetzner in Germany (EU). Emails are sent via Resend. The website is served via Cloudflare.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mt-8">Your rights</h2>
        <p>You can unsubscribe at any time. To request deletion of your data, email <a href="mailto:hello@cadre.run" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@cadre.run</a>.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mt-8">Contact</h2>
        <p>Cadre · Built in Germany · <a href="mailto:hello@cadre.run" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@cadre.run</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
